author: Source: Haringey Independent
title: Arsene Wenger praises 'intense and disciplined' Arsenal display against Bayern - Haringey Independent
text:
Arsene Wenger hailed his Arsenal side for their performance in a must-win game against Bayern Munich - but warned their Champions League fate still remains in the balance. Having opened their European campaign with consecutive defeats to Dynamo Zagreb and Olympiacos, the Gunners returned to form with a 2-0 victory over an in-form Bayern side courtesy of second-half goals from Olivier Giroud and Mesut Ozil.
 Haringey Independent.
